OL,3,CCold weather payments: What are they
OL,4,Cand could you be entitled to them?
OL,6,FThe UK is experiencing continued cold
OL,7,Ftemperatures, as well as its first
OL,8,Fnamed storm of 2026.
OL,10,FThe Met Office has issued several
OL,11,Fyellow and amber weather warnings on
OL,12,Faccount of Storm Goretti, cautioning
OL,13,Fthe public over snow and ice.
OL,15,FIts warnings also include advice to
OL,16,Fthe public that they should keep their
OL,17,Fhomes heated to a minimum of 18
OL,18,Fdegrees.
