OL,3,CCold weather payments: What are they
OL,4,Cand could you be entitled to them?
OL,6,FThose struggling to pay their energy
OL,7,Fbills could be entitled to further
OL,8,Fsupport from the government in the
OL,9,Fform of cold weather payments.
OL,11,FWhat are cold weather payments?
OL,13,FThe government provides #25 payments
OL,14,Fto people on specific benefits in
OL,15,Fareas where the average temperature is
OL,16,Frecorded as zero degrees or lower for
OL,17,Fseven consecutive days.
OL,19,FPeople can receive a #25 payment for
OL,20,Feach period of seven days that records
OL,21,Fthese temperatures.
