OL,3,CCold weather payments: What are they
OL,4,Cand could you be entitled to them?
OL,6,FPayments are made per household and
OL,7,Fnot per person, so only one payment
OL,8,Fwill be made even if multiple people
OL,9,Fin the same household qualify.
OL,11,FThe period for which households can be
OL,12,Feligible to receive the money runs
OL,13,Fbetween November 1 2025 and March 21
OL,14,F2026.
OL,16,FWho is eligible to claim?
OL,18,FOnly those who meet the criteria and
OL,19,Fare on certain benefits can receive
OL,20,Fthe payments.
