OL,3,CCold weather payments: What are they
OL,4,Cand could you be entitled to them?
OL,6,FThose in receipt of:
OL,8,FThose receiving JSA must also have
OL,9,Feither: A disability or pensioner
OL,10,Fpremium, a child who is disabled, or a
OL,11,Fchild under 5 living with them.
OL,13,FThose receiving ESA must also be in a
OL,14,Fwork-related activity group or support
OL,15,Fgroup. If they are not in either, they
OL,16,Fmight also get cold weather payments
